  Players in Team: %s

🎮 CHARACTER STATUS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Health: %s/%s
  WalkSpeed: %s
  State: %s
  Distance from You: %s studs

📊 LEADERSTATS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────
%s

🔗 QUICK LINKS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Friends: roblox.com/users/%d/friends
  Games: roblox.com/users/%d/games
